Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems rather avant-garde...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when I went \Nto rent videos from Wataru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looked interesting, so I couldn't \Nresist bringing it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to show it to \Nat least 2 people within a week
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! Isn't that the curse \Nfrom that loopish video?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way such \Nan unscientific thing could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even you have \Na rather childlike side to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain, just to be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The loopish video refers \Nto the movie "Ring"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Please don't say anything more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:24.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:27.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his \Nmistress in all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:29.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:33.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:37.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our theme may be horror, \Nwhich is typical for the Obon festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but perhaps I still acted too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Obon festival anyway. \NNo one's watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll go with animated storyboards \Nfor the rest of the episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:57.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:57.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:05.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:05.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:18.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:18.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:28.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:28.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:34.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:34.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:46.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:46.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:53.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:53.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:03:00.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:03:00.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Saki's Little Preoccupation \N(National Edition) 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that damn Nagi?! \NShe's late again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, she probably can't understand Oshii's \Nwork just watching it once, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That loopish video isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Horror Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea there were people kooky enough \Nto rent a knockoff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi's late again, so give her \Na call to remind her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since then, \Nbut nothing's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can't possibly be such \Nthings as ghosts in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria sure is something, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so mature. I bet there's nothing \Nthat she can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. We received \Na watermelon as a gift, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then let us be sure \Nto serve it to the Miss as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually took some to Nagi earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a better name \Nthat reaches out and grabs people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to incorporate horror \Nand develop a new genre!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to manga, \Nthe Miss gets too absorbed in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's also one \Nof her good qualities, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, you know, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Nagi's late again, so I'm here \Nto give her a little reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what was that weird video?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it. I noticed it was \Nmissing from the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Nagi took it \Nwithout letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made right around \Nwhen the original became a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Loop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knockoff and a pale imitation at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined anyone would want to \Nwatch something so obviously lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if Sadako comes \Nout of it, that's one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as I recall, when you watch that video,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thing that comes out is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, something like that would \Ncertainly be creepy, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki's been acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's got something on her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she won't even talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Just because she's turned 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is she trying to tell me that she \Ncan't turn to a 13-year-old for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki doesn't look it, but I guess her \Ncoming-of-age ceremony is next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming-of-age ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:55.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,329.6)}May of This Year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you're turning 20 in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should get you something \Nto mark the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sentiment alone is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always wearing a maid uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, want me to buy you \Na long-sleeved kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you really, Young Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're turning 20, you'll need one \Nfor the ceremony and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall look forward to it \Nwithout getting my hopes up too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because I forgot her birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and her long-sleeved kimono \Nfor her coming-of-age ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why she's depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are birthdays and \Ncoming-of-age ceremonies important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I imagine they're pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, how was your \Ncoming-of-age ceremony, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, r-right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still 17, so your \Nceremony's still a ways off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ROARRRR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a young and fresh \N17 years old, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you think I'd already had \Nmy coming-of-age ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria, you've been acting \Nstrange for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I haven't been acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I really wonder \Nwhat's gotten into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her coming-of-age ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just start \Nby asking Saki directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.96,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental \NV Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you sighing because \NI'd forgotten your birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nno one celebrated my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that it really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get back the time I've lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe I can win back the trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh... So what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'd ever give you a damn present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BA-BAM BAM BAM BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:04.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're asking a favor of someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as Haman Khan said, you would do well \Nto watch your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's better for her \Nto be playing nicely with her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than working on manga by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go see about \Ngetting these two some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's this about a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give someone \Na long-sleeved kimono as a present,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what kind to get her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho, a long-sleeved \Nkimono as a present, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so finally, you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cheap and they have \Nthe sort of kimono she'd like in stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll owe you one, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll head over there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but don't buy anything too cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you, just so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how much does one \Nlong-sleeved kimono cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it won't cost as much as 2 Ferraris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell does one outfit \Ncost more than a Ferrari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock the money sense \Nof the general public!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chair I hit you with earlier \Nwas even more expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of goods \Nare you using on a daily basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, once a man's decided \Nto give a woman a present,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,paying that kind of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a given! What's \Nthe point if you can't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure, that may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to get \Nthat kind of money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be in name only, \Nbut we're still betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No interest, pay it back \Nwhen you make it big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Roaches Come Come
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(544,237)}Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! An Onmyou mystic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, you're acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... Anything but that! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle anything but those \Nblack things that go scurrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea Maria had \Na side to her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. For losing my composure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the one thing that I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if {\i1}it{\i0} were to show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You will? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be all right, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach, roach, roach, \Nroach, roach, roach, roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am coming to be with you.\N({\u1}I{\u0}ma ai ni ikima{\u1}su{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can feel a draft.\N({\u1}Su{\u0}-Suusuu surun de{\u1}su{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea the Young Sir \Nwas so concerned about my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast to that, \NGranny hasn't even called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us explain this to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki Kijima's grandmother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:32.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...the legendary house maid, Rei Kijima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of her missing daughter \Nand her husband, i.e. Saki's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:40.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei Kijima went traveling across the world \Nwith her granddaughter, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At one time, she saved a president \Nfrom being assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:51.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At another time, she solved \Na difficult cold case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:57.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And on yet another occasion, \Nshe found an oppressed people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,whom she frequently freed \Nwith dishes that impressed the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:05.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, however, the legendary house maid \Nwas already 62 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Smack dab in the middle \Nof the Sahara Desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,she was on the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny! Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to let your \Nexhaustion overcome you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Rei Kijima, legendary house maid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is none other than the \Nleader of the Tachibana Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Enkyou Tachibana himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:28.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Enkyou rescued Rei Kijima \Nand also Saki, while he was at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A soul-deep rapport grows \Nbetween Rei Kijima and Enkyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,which is neither love nor friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:37.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And to repay him, Rei fights! \NAgainst evil! And against culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:41.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of all this, there was \Na new encounter for Saki, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her encounter with Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:49.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Being too young, the mother showed \Nalmost no interest in her own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:52.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing him in profile, \Nlooking so lonely, Saki swore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...that in thanks for rescuing Rei Kijima,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,she would repay them by raising \Nthis child to be a fine adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are. Tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:05.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To Saki, it seemed as though their two \Nsouls, abandoned by their mothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:08.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,were calling to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tea I make tastes better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Wataru turned out \Nto be an unexpectedly skillful boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,capable of doing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:22.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was far better at things \Nthan the naturally klutzy Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering how the Young Sir is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will I be able to guide him \Nso that he becomes a fine adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Saki's parents \Nlive in Ueno even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so please rest assured \Nthat they are not missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:42.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A d-dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:58.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, such a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On days like this, \Nthere is no better pastime
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to go around giving new \Nmeanings to the garden flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! Target sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Security
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Stream Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get him! We'll do \Nthe Jet Stream Attack one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Stream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep! He used me as a stepping stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be fine, \Nnow that we've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, anyone would have \Ndone the same in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one persistent bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lay a hand on Hayate \Nand you will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked big, saying I would protect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you ended up protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did protect me, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! If that thing goes after Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was thinking I had arrived \Nwithout getting lost for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I come to find a little one \Nwho has become lost in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi, I had no idea you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you see a black \Nscurrying thing around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that little one went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi defeated that thing...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear from Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's shy, \Nin spite of the way he acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it, a present \Nhas to come out of your own pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I looked at what \Nmy savings could buy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up with a summer kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what an adorable summer kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry... But what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Nagi said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you had something important \Nto say to me and a wonderful present,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I should come to your house right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the present be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what was the important \Nthing you had to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:59.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Nagi and her meddlesome ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a golden opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:05.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give this summer kimono to Isumi \Nand tell her how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,How I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get two \Nof the "Changéríon" box sets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was the important \Nthing you want to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about the performance of \NMr. Hagino, who plays the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from Asakura \Nin "Masked Rider Ryuki",
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his cheerful performance \Nis a real highlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take your time watching it \Nwhen you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Thank you, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, \NI felt bad for forgetting, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell another \Nwoman's scent in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you brought home a girl \Nwhile I was gone and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... did pervy things...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present for you! This summer kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why did you get me a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have enough money \Nand I couldn't buy a long-sleeved kimono,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this can't really take its place,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I forgot to get you a birthday present
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought maybe that's why \Nyou'd been so mopey lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that was bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was what color I should get \Nfor my new cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems that wasn't a present for Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you end up lending him money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it was pointless \Nif he didn't pay for it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it seems he bought a cheap summer \Nkimono instead of a long-sleeved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paid about 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fifty thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that loopish \Nthing hasn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Stuff like that is superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?! Did a missile \Ncome flying from somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They started a fireworks show nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, huh? Nothing says \Nsummer like fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go out together, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing says summer like grilled \Nsquid from a street stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You look good in that summer kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Young Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:19.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It just may be that yet another \Nnew misunderstanding has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, isn't it, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, a dragon and a hamster...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:50.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...will fight over the one they love \Nand their maidenly pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:22:00.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:22:00.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:05.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:05.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:08.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:08.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:12.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:12.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:29.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:29.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:38.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:38.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:47.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:47.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:51.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:51.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:10.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:10.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, \Nit'll be clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SIGN: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Cross Killer! I'm Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's really gotten hot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The highs in Nerima surpassed \N30 degrees Celsius today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make such offhand remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.26,0:23:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know if it'll be hot \Non the actual day this airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And depending on the region, \Nit'll air on different days, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. What I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that when it's hot, stay \Ncooped up in a room with A/C blasting,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,play some online game, \Nand listen to my character song!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't spend your summer \Nin such an unhealthy way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:23:58.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Starting today, \Nit's summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm going to play \Nonline games, watch anime, draw manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:19.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and have all the fun I want every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:06.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like her life is pretty similar, \Neven when she has school...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, summer break's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't feel very happy somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.44,0:24:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Like Books, But Sing It \NGreat Palace of the Dragon King".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:19.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that thieving hamster!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Like Books, But Sing It \NGreat Palace of the Dragon King
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:22.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you calling a thieving hamster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:24.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sign of the Guardian guides me.
